{
  "name": "Job Templates",
  "description": "Job Template management endpoints for creating templates, managing template fields, and organizing dynamic job workflows. Templates are the blueprint for Job instances.",
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Create Job Template",
      "request": {
        "auth": {
          "type": "bearer",
          "bearer": [
            {
              "key": "token",
              "value": "{{jwt_token}}",
              "type": "string"
            }
          ]
        },
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n    \"name\": \"Maintenance Job\",\n    \"description\": \"Standard maintenance workflow template for equipment servicing\",\n    \"isDefault\": false\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/job-templates",
          "host": [
            "{{base_url}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "api",
            "v1",
            "job-templates"
          ]
        },
        "description": "Create a new job template for the authenticated company.\n\n**Authentication:** Required (COMPANY role)\n\n**Request Body:**\n- name (string, required): Template name (2-150 characters, unique per company)\n- description (string, optional): Template description\n- isDefault (boolean, optional): Set as default template for the company (default: false). Only one template can be default per company.\n\n**Business Logic:**\n- Template is associated with the company of the authenticated user.\n- If isDefault is true, any existing default template will be unmarked as default.\n\n**Response:** Created template object with metadata (id, timestamps, archived flag, isDefault)."
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "Create Job Template - Success",
          "originalRequest": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"name\": \"Maintenance Job\",\n    \"description\": \"Standard maintenance workflow template for equipment servicing\"\n}"
            },
